quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Kamoe peutren nyan bak malam kadar
  97,2,Peue malam kadar jeut teuh tapeugah
  97,3,Malam kadar nyan siribee buleun Leubeh got lom nyan Neukheun le Allah
  97,4,Dum malaikat ngon roh malam nyan Geutron dum keunan ngon izin Allah Bandum urusan izin Po gopnyan
  97,5,Saleum ngon aman malam meutuah Malam nyan sampoe ‘an teubit fajar Malam mulia Neubri le Allah